Class AbstractPossibleSplit

  • java.lang.Object
    • rs.fon.whibo.problem.AbstractComponent

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryCategorical, BinaryNumerical, MultiwayCategorical, SignificantCategorical

    public abstract class AbstractPossibleSplit
extends AbstractComponent
implements PossibleSplit
    The Class AbstractPossibleSplit that is inherited by all Possible split components. As an input this class takes example set in current node and list of attributes that are available for possible split creation. As an output this class provides splitted example set (possible split for branching a tree) that is proceeded to Split Evaluation component.
